               <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3460"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__simon_von_retz_QGW_II_II_3460">Simon von Recz,
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_stephan">gracianer</roleName>
                        zu sand Stephan zu Wienn, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_niklas_vor_stubentor_kapelle-altar_fron-messe_mayr_otto">kaplan</roleName></rs>
                     <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II"><rs type="org" ref="org__wien-st_niklas_vor_stubentor_kapelle-altar_fron-messe_mayr_otto">der mess, die weilent Ott Mair auf dem Fronaltar, in sand Niclas kappeln
                           ausserhalb des klosters vor Stubentor hie zu Wienn in der Lanndtstrass
                           gelegen, gestifft hat</rs>,</rs></rs> so ihm <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="pe__oswald_reicholf_QGW_II_II_3314"><roleName type="title">her</roleName> Oswalt Reicholf, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burgermaister</roleName></rs>, und <rs type="org" ref="org__wien">der Rath</rs></rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">nach <add>abgang</add></triggerstring>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_poeltinger_QGW_II_II_3460"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Hannsen Pöltinger <roleName type="dead">abgang</roleName>
                        <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_niklas_vor_stubentor_kapelle-altar_fron-messe_mayr_otto"><add>Kaplan</add></roleName></rs></rs> durch goczwillen <triggerstring n="disp">verlihen habent, gelobt</triggerstring> diesen, <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_II"><rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_st_jakob_auf_der_huelben_1">das <roleName type="owner" corresp="org__wien-st_niklas_vor_stubentor_kapelle-altar_fron-messe_mayr_otto">zu der Messe gehörige</roleName> Haus <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-st_jakob_auf_der_huelben">bei sand
                        Jacob</roleName></rs></rs> in gutem baulichen Zustande <triggerstring n="disp">zu erhalten, die Gülten einzunehmen und die Messe stiftungsgemäss zu
                     lesen</triggerstring>.</rs>
            </p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3460"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Besiegelt mit
                     den Siegeln <rs type="person" ref="pe__konrad_strobel_QGW_II_II_3257">Conrats
                        des Strobel <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"><add>purger</add></roleName></rs> und <rs type="person" ref="pe__andreas_kelhaimer_QGW_II_II_3460">Andres des Kelhaimer, baid
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">purger</roleName> zu
                        Wienn</rs>.</rs></rs>
            </p></div><div type="nota"><p>Indorsate: a) verpuntnusse hern Simons, kaplan zu sand Niclas vor Stubentor, b) des
               Otmair stifft betreffend. </p></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>